Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么晚了还在散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了我专程去叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就不会感到痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫救命也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“炎发灼眼的讨伐者”也同意将你破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜她...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏远的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略微懂得一些操纵存在之力的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于破坏秘器一事你应该已经同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对我破坏秘器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能让“零时迷子”随机转移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能避免与“化装舞会”正面冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈的战斗只会使世界平衡崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到此 那是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不清楚敌人的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没掌握主动权的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将是最佳方案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也还要反对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这个感觉...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星黎殿”在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔菲戈那个老太婆和疯教授在到处折腾的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是动真格地想启动“灵魂殿堂”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会忙起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再能够静心祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其祈祷还不如求我 赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何为我所求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追求什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论问几次都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之就是无欲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她将被万物所追求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要“灵魂殿堂”启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那虽然不错 但真的不会伤害到赫卡特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 千变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特将会永生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有不一般的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是尽我的职责 保护我的赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是冰清玉洁的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你永远不变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚无一个红世之王做到的 存在之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然无法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请不要阻挠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜无法反对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏娜是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 万状饰者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事找那个秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情想问他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天不是说了两句关于徒的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 徒用过的鸟状饰物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 你就是想问那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事就想让我停止破坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一律视为无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘器有时会展示出非比寻常的洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的战斗中也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先听听比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种表情...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么坚持...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然对你们有用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个秘器应该还有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏延期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想对你失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没说完的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在担心留在城市中的鸟状饰物不知道要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被昨天的徒用作燐子的饰物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是幸存的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说还存在未知的危险性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说不知道徒袭来的意图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还没结束的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能排除这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有所警戒比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是秘器 夏娜是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再把这个城市和大家牵扯进战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为保护大家所能做的事 只有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护这个城市和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市和大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因为那种理由一起离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会离开城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使离开城市“化装舞会”也会追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的徒或许也会尾随而来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再去另一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要我战斗...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是想让我留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是要毁掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为火雾战士而言 那是一个正确的抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是的 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想让我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道夏娜你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡穆欣先生给了我一个护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 感觉到了封绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学 真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要离开这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下定决心有一部分原因是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过我是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想作为坂井悠二去保护珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想才是自己身为坂井悠二的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴吉田同学你对我的情意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真够强的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个 能够看到“封绝”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想或许大姐会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是说遇到徒的话就与之战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛乔里小姐离开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经和我们没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛乔里小姐也...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不得不赞同坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏还是保留
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开还是留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时就要拔剑对付“万状饰者”了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另一方面却竭力不想辜负她的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把坂井悠二怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说 希望坂井悠二怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那个零时什么的飞到其它地方去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 好像很难再次找到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“化装舞会”这个徒的团体也就不会来袭击御崎市了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你会...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学也...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 应该说是夏娜来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也说过要破坏你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜想怎么做我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士们都不把我们当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要离开城市的话 我跟你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种城市 那种家都没什么好留恋的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼不见为净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让坂井一个人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔回来一趟也是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 拖泥带水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有想见的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了就算了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开城市明明是一件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却能那么平静地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对由佳里同学也让她干脆点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为已经有一点点接近坂井同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 坂井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我更远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候开始不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在想破坏我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于火雾战士而言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终究只是个秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说不太对劲 就过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些饰物如果正常烧掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个女佣怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个秘器的眼光果然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用过一次的东西容易被忽略
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为以防万一 看着它们销毁殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:18:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都没感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 燃烧就是自在式发动的开关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳 那个自在式的上方会有东西到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时是飞艇...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星黎殿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“化装舞会”的大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“悖论裁决者”贝尔菲戈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 天壤劫火 万状饰者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你们也没察觉到这双重的机关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 火雾战士真是血气方刚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“化装舞会”的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔菲戈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的规模将对世界产生多大的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度就说是大规模...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世中威名远播的“天壤劫火”也落魄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始真正的大手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢欣赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里将成为存在之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是那种特意过来说闲话的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道他们的目标是“零时迷子”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍旧那么灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夺走之前先破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护秘器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁在“星黎殿”中的悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”引发前所未有的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.74,0:24:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寄予了希望的夏娜面临决断之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.05,0:24:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇曳之炎
